Name: extrahepatic bile duct adenocarcinoma
Definition: An extrahepatic bile duct carcinoma that derives_from epithelial cells of glandular origin.
Synonym: adenocarcinoma of the extrahepatic bile duct

Name: extrahepatic bile duct leiomyosarcoma
Definition: A leiomyosarcoma and sarcoma of bile duct that is located_in the bile duct or located_in the outside of the liver.

Name: obsolete vessel leiomyosarcoma
Definition: A leiomyosarcoma and sarcoma of bile duct that is located_in the bile duct or located_in the outside of the liver.
